comment: Parker (SAS) makes incidental contact with Beal (WAS) as they attempt to grab the loose ball.
Aldridge (SAS) bumps Wall (WAS) and affects his shooting movement.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Porter (WAS) was the last player to touch the ball before it went OOB was upheld.
Duncan (SAS) establishes a legal screening position in Beal's (WAS) path outside his field of vision, giving him a step towards him. Contact occurs with Duncan's upper body while he is firming up.
Porter (WAS) makes incidental contact with Leonard (SAS) after he releases the shot.
Duncan (SAS) commits a take foul on Wall (WAS).
